{"metadata":{"name":"Sunan an Nasai","section":{"48":"The Book of Adornment"},"section_detail":{"48":{"hadithnumber_first":5040,"hadithnumber_last":5378,"arabicnumber_first":5040,"arabicnumber_last":5378}}},"hadiths":[{"hadithnumber":5237,"arabicnumber":5237,"text":"Rapporté par Abu Qatadah : Il avait de longs cheveux épais. Il a demandé au Prophète ﷺ à ce sujet et il lui a dit de les entretenir et de les peigner chaque jour","grades":[{"name":"Abu Ghuddah","grade":"Daif"},{"name":"Al-Albani","grade":"Daif"},{"name":"Zubair Ali Zai","grade":"Daif"}],"reference":{"book":48,"hadith":198}}]}